{"tid":1324732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術JJ]有冇人試過整TATP","createTime":"2019-07-16T15:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:19:07.000Z","uid":271981,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"050659590ed3e67cb3d19b96caa1e3a6763a149f","tid":1324732,"uid":271981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"From wiki<br />\n//三過氧化三丙酮（英語：Triacetone triperoxide，簡稱TATP）是一種有機過氧化物起爆藥及二甲基過氧化酮的閉環三聚體，起爆力介於雷汞與疊氮化鉛之間。曾考慮用作雷管裝藥，但因其易於昇華的特性（於室溫放置兩週，質量損失可達66%[1]）兼高機械感度，在商業與軍事上並未得到廣泛應用。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%89%E9%81%8E%E6%B0%A7%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%99%E9%85%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25B0%25A7%25E5%258C%2596%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25B8%2599%25E9%2585%25AE&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=361ae6c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%89%E9%81%8E%E6%B0%A7%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%99%E9%85%AE</a><br />\n香港整會唔會犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7644f02e0f5fa0f2d0df267138027e9758280729","tid":1324732,"uid":271981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c10f9c5861b4b47f3296a9aadc179010c8393b0","tid":1324732,"uid":271981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cac9dbc24b4e775815b64e1b1f6642f9238b27","tid":1324732,"uid":271981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SELMWWm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSELMWWm.jpg&h=80d6d25b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45595b43bd02ca7ebb2f4bb22a938ff